---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — A Day In">
  <PageHeader
    label="About us"
    title="The best adventure isn't found where everyone else is."
    description="A dream for more adventure in a world of checklist-based tourism."
  />
  
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-14 sm:px-8">
    <div class="prose-sea">
      <p>
        <strong>A Day In</strong> is built on a simple idea: the best story doesn't come from an "I've been there" brag, it comes from sharing a journey to somewhere people have never heard of and the unexpected things that came between. The places off the beaten track, the ones a little difficult to get to, and the memories that make us want to go back after.
      </p>
      <p>
        Throughout our travels, we discovered that the trips we look most fondly at, are the ones where we picked a direction and winged the rest. The journey's where we underestimated how long it would take to walk there or what was inbetween. These are the days we always remember, more than the days where we tried to cram the "top 20 must see things" into one day.
      </p>
      <p>
        A Day In hopes to bridge the gap between those "top 10 must see" lists with hand crafted day itineraries. Aiming to get you out of your comfort zone and get you exploring on your own, while still feeling like it's something you can do.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
